00:10:59.900 --> 00:11:09.590
So now it's time for you to see
the Spanish incarnation of the U.S.

00:11:09.590 --> 00:11:10.890
and the Mexican Revolution.

00:11:10.890 --> 00:11:13.510
So, Tracy North, you're up.

00:11:13.510 --> 00:11:17.510
[ Laughter ]

00:11:17.510 --> 00:11:28.380
[ Applause ]

00:11:28.380 --> 00:11:30.250
&gt;&gt; Tracy North: Thank you.

00:11:30.250 --> 00:11:33.410
So as Dr. Tenenbaum stated,
many people have worked

00:11:33.410 --> 00:11:37.040
on this online exhibition
over the past several years.

00:11:37.040 --> 00:11:39.930
I came along toward the end
and have been involved just

00:11:39.930 --> 00:11:42.700
