launch the site.

00:11:42.700 --> 00:11:46.660
We did launch the English version
of the redesigned site in February

00:11:46.660 --> 00:11:48.650
of this year, and we're here today

00:11:48.650 --> 00:11:52.440
to celebrate the launch
