viewing and looks phenomenal

00:12:11.030 --> 00:12:16.810
on phones, iPads, all the way
up through desktop computers.

00:12:16.810 --> 00:12:20.470
So please, after today,
go take a look at it.

00:12:20.470 --> 00:12:23.420
You will be impressed,
I guarantee you.

