Congress on Facebook or on Twitter.

00:13:20.090 --> 00:13:22.420
You can follow our 4 Corners blog

00:13:22.420 --> 00:13:24.920
where we highlight
international collections.

00:13:24.920 --> 00:13:28.070
In all of these places, we have
been highlighting this Mexican

00:13:28.070 --> 00:13:30.250
Revolution project.

00:13:30.250 --> 00:13:33.140
And you can also visit
our website directly.

00:13:33.140 --> 00:13:37.790
If you go to the exhibitions home
page and then click on the link

00:13:37.790 --> 00:13:41.530
